  <brief_title>Development of the Partial Pressure of Carbon Dioxide During Exercise and at Night in Patients With Chronic Obstructive Pulmonary Disease (COPD) IV</brief_title>
  <official_title>Development of the Partial Pressure of Carbon Dioxide During 6-min Walking Test and at Night in Patients With Chronic Obstructive Pulmonary Disease IV</official_title>
